import csv
import math
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import scipy.fftpack
from scipy.signal import find_peaks
from scipy.fftpack import fft, ifft
from ipywidgets import widgets, interact, interactive
from IPython.display import display

lim_end = 6000

filenamesano = '7.csv'
data1 = pd.read_csv(filenamesano, header=0)
sano = data1['MLII']
ysano = sano.tolist()
ysano = np.array(ysano)

fs = 360  # Frecuencia de muestreo
x = np.arange(0, float(len(ysano)) / fs, 1.0 / fs)
x = x[0:lim_end]
ysano = ysano[0:lim_end]

# Gráfica 1: Señal del electrocardiograma
plt.figure(figsize=(14, 4))
plt.grid()
plt.xlim(0, 10)
plt.plot(x, ysano)
plt.title("Señal del electrocardiograma")
plt.xlabel("Tiempo (Seg)")
plt.ylabel("Amplitud")
plt.grid(True)
plt.show()

# Calcula la Transformada de Fourier de la señal con ruido
yf = scipy.fftpack.fft(ysano)
xf = np.linspace(0.0, 1.0 / (2.0 * (1.0 / fs)), len(ysano) // 2)

# Gráfica 2: Espectro de Señal
plt.figure(figsize=(14, 4))
plt.grid(True)
plt.xlim(0, 70)
plt.ylim(0, 50)
plt.plot(xf, 2.0 / lim_end * np.abs(yf[:len(ysano) // 2]))
plt.title("Espectro de Señal")
plt.xlabel("Frecuencia (Hz)")
plt.ylabel("Amplitud")
plt.show()

frechz = 50

def denoise_signal(data, L=10):
    coefs = np.ones(L) / float(L)
    smoothed_signal = np.convolve(data, coefs, mode='same')
    return smoothed_signal

noise_free_healthy = denoise_signal(sano)
noise_free_healthy = noise_free_healthy[frechz:lim_end - frechz]

# Encuentra los picos en la señal noise_free_healthy
peak_indices, _ = find_peaks(noise_free_healthy, height=(np.mean(noise_free_healthy)+100, 2000))


# Extrae los valores de los picos y sus correspondientes tiempos
peak_values = noise_free_healthy[peak_indices]
peak_times = x[frechz:lim_end - frechz][peak_indices]

# Gráfica 3: Señal noise_free_healthy
plt.figure(figsize=(14, 4))
plt.plot(x[frechz:lim_end - frechz], noise_free_healthy)
plt.title("Señal Filtrada")
plt.xlabel("Tiempo (Seg)")
plt.ylabel("Amplitud")
plt.grid(True)
plt.show()

# Gráfica 4: Picos en noise_free_healthy
plt.figure(figsize=(14, 4))
plt.plot(x[frechz:lim_end - frechz], noise_free_healthy, alpha=0.8)
plt.scatter(peak_times, peak_values, color='red', marker='o', label='Picos')
plt.grid()
plt.title('Deteccion de picos')
plt.xlabel("Tiempo (Seg)")
plt.ylabel("Amplitud")
plt.legend()
plt.show()

def normalize_signal(signal):
    normalized_signal = (signal - np.mean(signal))
    normalized_signal = normalized_signal / np.max(normalized_signal)
    return normalized_signal

def classify_arrhythmia(age, condition, heart_rate):
    age = int(age)
    if condition == "Si":
        active = 1
    else:
        active = 0


    if age >= 5 and age <= 6:
        if heart_rate < 75:
            return "Presenta Bradicardia Infantil"
        else:
            if heart_rate > 115:
                return "Presenta Taquicardia Infantil"
            else:
                return "Estado normal"

    if age >= 7 and age <= 9:
        if heart_rate < 70:
            return "Presenta bradicardia Infantil"
        else:
            if heart_rate > 110:
                return "Presenta Taquicardia Infantil"
            else:
                return "Negativo, no presenta arritmia"

    if age >= 10:
        if active == 0:
            if heart_rate < 60:
                return "Presenta Bradicardia"
            else:
                if heart_rate > 100:
                    return "Presenta Taquicardia"
                else:
                    return "Estado normal"
        else:
             if heart_rate < 40:
                return "Presenta Bradicardia"
             else:
                if heart_rate > 60:
                    return "Presenta Taquicardia"
                else:
                    return "Negativo, no presenta arritmia"

def additional_info(coef):

    if coef == 1:
        return "No presenta alertas"

    if coef <= 3.86e-04:
        return "Cuidado, posible bloqueo en la rama izquierda por presunto infarto agudo al miocardio. Diríjase al hospital más cercano."

    if coef >= 0.015 and coef <=0.038:
        return "Fibrilación auricular. Diríjase al hospital más cercano."

    if coef <= 0.49:
        return "Cuidado, posible infarto agudo al miocardio con elevación del segmento ST."



def process_ecg_data(filename_patient, age, condition):
    plt.rcParams["figure.figsize"] = (5, 3)
    plt.rcParams['lines.linewidth'] = 1
    plt.rcParams['lines.color'] = 'b'
    plt.rcParams['axes.grid'] = True

    fs = 360
    lim_end = 2500
    frechz = 50

    # Reference healthy patient
    filename_healthy = '7.csv'
    data_healthy = pd.read_csv(filename_healthy, header=0)
    healthy_data = data_healthy['MLII']
    y_healthy = healthy_data.tolist()
    y_healthy = np.array(y_healthy)
    x = np.arange(0, float(len(y_healthy)) / fs, 1.0 / fs)
    x = x[0:lim_end]
    y_healthy = y_healthy[0:lim_end]

    # Data of the patient to process
    data_patient = pd.read_csv(filename_patient, header=0)
    patient_data = data_patient['MLII']
    y_patient = patient_data.tolist()
    y_patient = y_patient[0:lim_end]

    noise_free_healthy = denoise_signal(y_healthy)
    noise_free_healthy = noise_free_healthy[frechz:lim_end - frechz]

    noise_free_patient = denoise_signal(y_patient)
    noise_free_patient = noise_free_patient[frechz:lim_end - frechz]

    # Create subplots for the plots
    fig, axs = plt.subplots(2, 1, figsize=(8, 8))

    # Plot of the patient's signal
    axs[0].plot(x[frechz:lim_end - frechz], noise_free_patient)
    axs[0].set_title('Patient Signal')

    # Correlation to find the heart rate in the patient
    one = normalize_signal(noise_free_patient)
    one_corr = np.correlate(one, one, 'full')
    tau_corr = np.arange(float((-len(one) + 1) / fs), float(len(one) / fs), 1.0 / fs)

    # Plot of the correlation
    axs[1].plot(tau_corr, one_corr)
    axs[1].set_title('Correlation')

    maxval = np.max(one_corr)
    peaks, _ = find_peaks(one_corr, height=maxval * 0.40)
    tmp = tau_corr[peaks]
    heart_rate_calc = int(60 / np.abs(np.abs(tmp[0]) - np.abs(tmp[1])))

    result1 = classify_arrhythmia(age, condition, heart_rate_calc)

    two = normalize_signal(noise_free_healthy)

    coef = np.corrcoef(one, two)
    correlation_one_two = coef[0, 1]
    result2 = additional_info(np.absolute(coef[1][0]))



    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()

    print("Resultado prueba de arritmia:", result1)
    print("Diagnóstco preventivo:", result2)
    print("Frecuencia Cardiaca:", heart_rate_calc)

    return heart_rate_calc, result1, result2

# GUI
def process_ecg_gui(file_name, age, condition):
    process_ecg_data(file_name, age, condition)

# Create widgets
file_name_widget = widgets.Text(value='archivo.csv', description='Ingresa aquí el nombre del archivo .csv dado el hospital:', style={'description_width': 'initial'})
file_name_widget.layout.width = '450px'  # Ajusta el ancho según sea necesario
age_widget = widgets.IntSlider(value=20, min=1, max=100, step=1, description='Ingresa tu edad:', style={'description_width': 'initial'})
condition_widget = widgets.Dropdown(options=['Si', 'No'], value='Si', description='¿Eres una persona activa físicamente?:', style={'description_width': 'initial'})

# Create processing button
process_button = widgets.Button(description='Consulta tu resultado')
process_button.on_click(lambda b: process_ecg_gui(file_name_widget.value, age_widget.value, condition_widget.value))

# Display widgets
display(file_name_widget)
display(age_widget)
display(condition_widget)
display(process_button)
